        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-note icon=false}\n",
        "## Definition 9.3 — GARCH(1,1) Stationarity and Unconditional Variance\n",
        "\n",
        "The GARCH(1,1) process is covariance-stationary if and only if:\n",
