        "\n",
        "### The ARCH($\\infty$) Equivalence\n",
        "\n",
        "The claim that GARCH(1,1) is equivalent to an ARCH($\\infty$) with geometrically\n",
        "declining weights deserves a brief demonstration, because it explains why a\n",
